Fresh facts have emerged on the unfulfilled plans of late Dayo Kujore’s during his burial, which is ongoing in his hometown, Ignore Robiyna, Abeokuta, Ogun State. The Nation gathered the late singer had planned to relocate to the United States of America before his sudden demise. It was further disclosed that the ‘Soko Xtra’ star recently had his first legal marriage to his last wife.   I’m doing all that makes me happy in 2022 –…     It’s degrading calling me Wizkid’s third baby mama- Jada…     Juju musician Dayo Kujore goes home   The marriage had prompted his unfulfilled plans of relocating to the United States of America to settle down with his new wife. - Advertisement - “He was planning to relocate and settle down in America before death disagreed with him”, a source told The Nation. “His most recent legal marriage to his last wife was part of his relocation plans”. The source also revealed that Kujore recently moved into his newly built home in Iyana Ilogbo, Ogun State.